parent: pm-gantt-chart-35p0
body: "Symptom: default `--group-by milestone` lumps every item under \"(no milestone)\".\nRepro: seed items with `--sprint M1/M2`, run `pm gantt`.\nObserved: one group \"(no milestone)\".\nExpected: items grouped by their sprint/release.\nRoot cause: pm has no `milestone` field; code read item.milestone -> always undefined.\nFix: itemMilestone() maps milestone grouping onto item.milestone ?? sprint ?? release. Verified: groups M1/M2/(no milestone), groupCount 3."
